WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.563 --> 00:00:03.936
Supply chain management must embrace customer service

2
00:00:03.936 --> 00:00:06.130
in order to be successful.

3
00:00:06.130 --> 00:00:08.211
We must communicate with our customers

4
00:00:08.211 --> 00:00:10.914
with the highest degree of professionalism,

5
00:00:10.914 --> 00:00:14.144
ensure their needs are satisfied, and be approachable,

6
00:00:14.144 --> 00:00:18.016
courteous, friendly, kind, and empathetic.

7
00:00:18.016 --> 00:00:20.712
We must respond to our customers in a timely manner

8
00:00:20.712 --> 00:00:22.799
and provide solutions.

9
00:00:22.799 --> 00:00:25.797
We must follow up an issue from start to finish

10
00:00:25.797 --> 00:00:29.374
and especially, must be flexible in addressing issues.

11
00:00:29.374 --> 00:00:32.848
Consistency builds trust and all SCM staff

12
00:00:32.848 --> 00:00:37.015
must always take the extra step to complete any task.

